ca.mcgill.ecse321.scorekeeper.model

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse321.scorekeeper.model.Game

  • public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    Domain object that stores data relating a Game. Two teams play a Game. Each Game takes place in a League.
    See Also:
    Team, League
